nodes.text: Asset SF-5, also referred to as Shroud SF-5, was a member of the intelligence network that served the independent operative known as the Shroud during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. Asset SF-5 was sent to the Kuat Drive Yards to dispose of Shroud SF-4's body and belongings, and to observe the outcome of the Battle of Kuat.
